          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/tracki-2021-model-mini-real-time-gps-tracker-920212.jpg",
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "DON'T BE FOOLED BY BLUETOOTH TRACKERS",
            "description": "<p>With a Tracki® device, easily track people, cars or assets in real time.  Tracki®  Worldwide GPS Tracker allows you to monitors location with pinpoint accuracy and track anywhere discreetly while giving you real-time updates.</p>",
