      "blocks": {
        "1644818997c04c6254-0": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>This is an excellent device, accurate reliable and works great. I found the device and subscription price to be way better than all the other GPS trackers. I had few questions and customer service was great.</p>",
            "author": "Russell",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "1644818997c04c6254-1": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>Yet another great customer service experience with \"Glen\" - He handled all my inquiries, needs and even informed me (to which he also signed me up as well), for Tracki's Lifetime Warranty. He informed me that the Lifetime warranty comes with purchasing Tracki through Amazon- they will replace the device if lost/stolen or ceases to function- and Tracki has already replaced the first device I purchased (it got lost, or I hid it so well I couldn't find it and the battery died, lol!</p>",
            "author": "Eric",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "1644818997c04c6254-2": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>I purchased the Tracki with suspicion of my husband’s activity and thanks for the Tracki I was correct, it was a great device and works amazing, I highly recommend it!</p>",
            "author": "Victoria",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
